{"article_id":"Q1VGVrFGtdzYu2Fd","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON ( ) -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Former FBI Director James Comey in memos","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"recounting conversations with U.S. President Donald Trump last year","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"said","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"Trump repeatedly raised concern over salacious allegations in an intelligence dossier , the need for loyalty and ferreting out leakers .","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"The partially redacted memos were handed over on Thursday by the U.S. Justice Department to three House of Representatives committees .","depth":4},{"id":6,"text":"The memos ,","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"seen by ,","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"include notes on a meeting at the Trump Tower in New York in January 2017 just before Trump ' s inauguration","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"in which Comey spoke alone with the then president-elect about the dossier","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"that detailed an alleged 2013 encounter","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"involving Trump and prostitutes in Moscow .","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"\" James Comey Memos just out","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"and show clearly","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"that there was NO COLLUSION and NO OBSTRUCTION .","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"Also , he leaked classified information .","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"WOW !","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"Will the Witch Hunt continue ? , \"","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"Trump said in a Tweet .","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"The memos also describe a dinner","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"Comey and Trump had at the White House about a week after the inauguration ,","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"when Comey said","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"Trump told him","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"he expected loyalty from him .","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"Trump fired Comey in May 2017","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"while Comey was leading the FBI investigation into allegations of Russian interference in the 2016 U.S. presidential election and possible collusion between Trump ' s campaign and the Russians .","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"The Comey ' s memos were written before his firing ,","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"which led to the appointment of Special Counsel Robert Mueller","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"to continue the investigation .","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"Russia denies any meddling in the election .","depth":5},{"id":30,"text":"Trump says","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"there was no collusion","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"and that the investigation is a witch hunt .","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"Much of the memo ' s contents were included in a book by Comey","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"titled \" A Higher Loyalty :","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"Truth , Lies and Leadership \"","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"and published this week","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"in which he compares the Republican president to a mob boss","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"who stresses personal loyalty over the law","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"and has little regard for morality or truth .","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"In one memo , Comey recounts a Feb. 8 , 2017 , meeting with then-White House Chief of Staff Reince Priebus ,","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"about two weeks after acting Attorney General Sally Yates had warned the White House","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"that Michael Flynn , then Trump ' s national security adviser , had lied about his December 2016 conversation with the Russian ambassador to the United States .","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"Comey wrote in the memo","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"that Priebus asked","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"\" if this was a ' private conversation. ' \"","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"Priebus then asked :","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"\" Do you have a FISA order on Mike Flynn ? \"","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"referring to the Foreign Intelligence Surveillance Act ,","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"according to the memo .","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"At the White House dinner in January , Comey said","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"Trump told him","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"that Flynn \" has serious judgment issues. \"","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"Comey said","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"Trump ' s comment came","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"after he learned","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"there was a delay","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"in returning a congratulatory phone call from a foreign leader .","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"According to a memo in mid-February ,","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"Priebus requested","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"that Comey and other senior FBI officials \" publicly knock down media reports about communications between Donald Trump ' s associates and Russians","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"known to U.S. intelligence during the 2016 presidential campaign. \"","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"They declined to do so .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":125,"left":0,"right":124,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":124,"left":85,"right":123,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":85,"left":67,"right":84,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":67,"left":66,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":66,"left":65,"right":4,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":65,"left":64,"right":3,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":64,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":84,"left":79,"right":83,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":79,"left":72,"right":78,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":72,"left":68,"right":71,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":68,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":71,"left":8,"right":70,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":70,"left":9,"right":69,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":69,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":78,"left":77,"right":18,"relation